  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Design specifically for mobile viewport/React Native Expo guidelines but use provided standard tokens.",
    "Use JetBrains Mono for all numeric values (Balances, Hash Rates, Prices) to achieve the technical fintech feel.",
    "Apply 'pulse-glow' animation to the Active Mining Machine card using Reanimated or CSS keyframes.",
    "Do NOT use pure white for the background. Stick strictly to #0B0E14 for main backgrounds to maintain contrast.",
    "For the bottom navigation, use a glassmorphism effect (blur + semi-transparent bg) and highlight the active icon with #00FFA3.",
    "Wrap interactive elements with 'data-testid' for testing (e.g., data-testid='withdraw-btn').",
    "Use Phosphor Icons, Lucide React, or @expo/vector-icons for crisp iconography matching the premium look."
  ]
